⁠𝔸𝕦𝕥𝕠 ℂ𝕚𝕟𝕕𝕖𝕣𝕖𝕝𝕝𝕒 𝕁𝕒𝕔𝕜 is strong and compact and filled from head to toe with sticky flowers with a good flower-to-leaf ratio. 🌻🌿⁠
⁠
This project originally started with a crossing of ℂ𝕚𝕟𝕕𝕖𝕣𝕖𝕝𝕝𝕒 𝟡𝟡 and 𝕁𝕒𝕔𝕜 ℍ𝕖𝕣𝕖𝕣. Auto genetics were used from the “𝕄𝕒𝕘𝕟𝕦𝕞" genetic line. 🧬⁠
⁠
📸 These beautiful shots were taken by @antonioo_cc ⁠

node.text:
What a fantastic view for these ⁠Auto Skywalker Hαze plants in the south of France! 😍⁠ 🇫🇷 ⁠ ⁠
⁠
Auto Skywalker Hαze is a Sativα-dominant hybrid autoflower with a hybrid plant and leaf structure that clearly leans more towards the Sativα side of the genes. Like many Sativα dominant plants, it is a real 'light lover'. This means that she can handle high light levels and a lot of (sun)light. ☀️⁠
⁠
🌱 These beauties were organically grown with @biotabs_official ⁠
🔗 More info - link in our bio⁠
⁠
#beautifulview #weekend #goodvibes #bluesky #sungrown

node.text:
Ever grown a classic variety with memorably epic results, only to find out the variety has subsequently been discontinued? ❌⁠
⁠
The good news is that sometimes your favourite discontinued strains have a close genetic match. Dutch Passion have been around since the 1980’s. In that time, some very special varieties have come and gone. If you have ever wanted to see a legendary variety re-emerge like a phoenix, then this blog is just for you! 🔥⁠⁠
⁠
📗 Read more in our blog⁠
🔗 Link in our story & bio ⁠
⁠
#discontinued #blog #genetics #fridayfeeling #fridayvibes #fridayfun
